Hundreds of pop quizzes may have said I failed, but my moral compass says otherwise. Reductress* Reads'.

Was it Mrs. Reynolds? But you know what, maybe the question should be why were we only assigned Black-written texts about slavery? Damn. Yeah. Bet you didn't think about that. Better luck next time. Reductress' Reads'.

Reductress Reads'.

Mystery as a genre is fascist in general. Kangaroo Jack is a misrepresentation of what it's like to be antagonized by a kangaroo (speaking from lived experience). All Nancy Meyers movies are problematic, and not because they re about rich white people, but because my ex loved them and they cheated on me. They're also fascist. Reductress* Reads'.

When you do this I will get extremely defensive, and I love in- teracting with the world this way. Here's to life and art, and death to Kangaroo Jack apologists! Reductress' Reads'.
